{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_07_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜の恋愛ゲームが発売して数日後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9533.3333333,
          "startTime": 9.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "この選択肢はどっちを選べば……\nここはあえて怜の誘いを断ってみるか",
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333400001,
          "startTime": 10.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？\n何をしているんですか？",
      "startTime": 13.8666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "何って、見ての通り、サンプルでもらった\n怜の恋愛ゲームをプレイしているんだ",
      "startTime": 18.8000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事中に何をしてるんですか！\n恥ずかしいのでやめて下さい！",
      "startTime": 24.2333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、こうやって確認するのも\nマネージャーの仕事だから……おっと、また選択肢だ",
      "startTime": 28.8333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "やめて下さい！\nせめて私の見てる前ではやらないで下さい！",
      "startTime": 35.9333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに恥ずかしがらなくてもいいと思うが……",
      "startTime": 39.2333343347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "身内にデート現場を見られてるみたいで\nこっちがいたたまれない気分になるんです！",
      "startTime": 45.8000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "最近はサニピのみんなもこのゲームで遊んでいて\n面と向かって私に感想を言ってくるんですよ",
      "startTime": 52.6666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今朝なんて雫から「恋する怜ちゃん……可愛い……\nギャップ萌え最高……！」って熱弁されて……",
      "startTime": 61.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらさくらが「ギャップじゃないよ\n怜ちゃんはいつも可愛いよ」って言い出して……",
      "startTime": 70.0002138317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そのままみんなで私の可愛いポイントをあげ始めて……\n毎日恥ずかしい思いをしてるんですから！",
      "startTime": 79.7666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず仲がいいな。それはそうと、このゲーム\nかなり話題になっているそうじゃないか",
      "startTime": 87.7666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、まぁ……\n反響が大きくて私も驚いてます",
      "startTime": 93.1828036829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさんに楽しんでもらえるか心配だったので\n思ってたよりも評判が良くてホッとしました",
      "startTime": 100.9333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでもらえて良かったな\nん？　そういえば、今日の怜の服装は……",
      "startTime": 107.3666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "気が付きましたか？\nこれ、ゲームの中の私が着ていた服と同じなんですよ",
      "startTime": 113.7333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのプロモーション用にって衣装さんが\n同じ服を作ってくれたんです",
      "startTime": 121.6333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "今日もこの後、ゲームの仕事があるので\n着て来ちゃいました",
      "startTime": 126.6495872338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　似合いますか？",
      "startTime": 128.5333363692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、よく似合ってるよ\n本当にゲームの中から怜が出てきたみたいだ",
      "startTime": 134.4333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今にも美味しいお弁当を出してくれそうな気がするよ",
      "startTime": 137.7333363692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……！？\nそれは現実の私には出来ないって意味ですか……？",
      "startTime": 143.1666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、そういう意味で言った訳じゃないぞ！",
      "startTime": 149.0666697025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "あれはあくまで『一ノ瀬怜』というキャラクターです！",
      "startTime": 152.1333363692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、ゲームの中の私は料理上手で\n好きな人のためにお弁当を作ったりしてましたけど……",
      "startTime": 160.6666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "それは嘘をついている訳じゃなくて、こうなれたら\nっていう私の願望も入れてもらったんです！",
      "startTime": 168.057790067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "それに私だってあのくらいの料理、やろうと思えば……\nって何か言いたげな目をしてますね？",
      "startTime": 177.540906459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、こうなりたいという願望も含めて\nありのままの怜ってことだよな。いいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 185.5000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "その言い方なんか腑に落ちません……",
      "startTime": 189.7333363692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだ！　沢山怜の希望が反映されているんだろ？\n特に気に入っているシーンとかあるのか？",
      "startTime": 198.2666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "どの場面も好きですけど……一つ選ぶなら\nテーマパークに行くシーンでしょうか",
      "startTime": 205.4666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "私はテーマパークが好きで\n小さい頃は家族でよく遊びに行っていました",
      "startTime": 212.7666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "私がダンスを始めたきっかけも、テーマパークの\nステージで踊るキャストに憧れたからです",
      "startTime": 220.2938286847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "だからこのシーンは特に\n現実の私とリンクしている気がして……",
      "startTime": 226.1333558399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームの中だけど、夢が叶ったみたいで嬉しかったです",
      "startTime": 229.5666849612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\n怜はこういうデートをするのが夢だったのか",
      "startTime": 237.0666769662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_03-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　ち、違います！\n何勝手にデートの話だと勘違いしてるんですか！",
      "startTime": 243.6666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
